      <title>[We forget all the time, and one day our name will never be spoken again. But at...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DVjEYPsDZj1/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/646001351_18438098746119929_8787189222944522820_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0NjkzNDg3NDM0NzY1ODM4NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEyNzl4ODU5LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=87KYQ1xqHzMQ7kNvwH3KDRL&amp;_nc_oc=AdoUyFKLOl4CwlJznG0hOZ1dm2ANpITozgVhkdAI-20jFkq6NLT2_WVAqbnjqWyMjYg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=HokE_Qqg0vvvcz532z231g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfynilUC7oISCx8s7VLHlv4KQeU8C8mfMWZgUN1vrnAGhQ&amp;oe=69C9AF69" alt="Instagram billede fra @siyan_siyan_siyan" /></p><p><strong>@siyan_siyan_siyan</strong></p><p>[We forget all the time, and one day our name will never be spoken again. But at least, for me, this moment was captured, so I can remember again.<br/>
I truly love the people I share laughter and tears with — and isn‘t that what life is all about? Love?<br/>
thanks for the lovely pictures @hannahqzhu <br/>
The day I forget and now they come back to me and put a smile on my face. ❤️</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/646001351_18438098746119929_8787189222944522820_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0NjkzNDg3NDM0NzY1ODM4NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEyNzl4ODU5LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=87KYQ1xqHzMQ7kNvwH3KDRL&amp;_nc_oc=AdoUyFKLOl4CwlJznG0hOZ1dm2ANpITozgVhkdAI-20jFkq6NLT2_WVAqbnjqWyMjYg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=HokE_Qqg0vvvcz532z231g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfynilUC7oISCx8s7VLHlv4KQeU8C8mfMWZgUN1vrnAGhQ&amp;oe=69C9AF69" alt="Instagram billede fra @siyan_siyan_siyan" /></p><p><strong>@siyan_siyan_siyan</strong></p><p>[We forget all the time, and one day our name will never be spoken again. But at least, for me, this moment was captured, so I can remember again.<br/>
I truly love the people I share laughter and tears with — and isn‘t that what life is all about? Love?<br/>
thanks for the lovely pictures @hannahqzhu <br/>
The day I forget and now they come back to me and put a smile on my face. ❤️</p>]]></content:encoded>
