      <title>Jungle Butterfly (@siyan_siyan_siyan) is a musician from Chongqing, the mountain...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DPNpUGIAI-w/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/556462724_18367344148159974_6132829777560665436_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=MzczMjgyMTM1NzU4NzYyOTkxNA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Jq6XT6feTdEQ7kNvwGgLBL_&amp;_nc_oc=AdrQueRhfF0vQdUSfPUL-t5R-loM81NmpmY0Dq_6tkOILrCpXHuOEaXT1h2Gj_YFvs0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=HokE_Qqg0vvvcz532z231g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzQH9K79YS4cKLjwxzOKriy6rjKcT7fwVHVEwxzOCqfrQ&amp;oe=69C998E1" alt="Instagram billede fra @siyan_siyan_siyan" /></p><p><strong>@siyan_siyan_siyan</strong></p><p>Jungle Butterfly (@siyan_siyan_siyan) is a musician from Chongqing, the mountain city where bridges, rivers, and ridgelines shaped her world. Blending Western electronic dance with Chinese cultural elements, she’s bringing her unique Eastern voice to the global stage.<br/>
<br/>
Chongqing is often seen as a neon-soaked cyberpunk city, but her guide shows the other side: a softer, more natural rhythm. Evening walks and breezes on E’gongyan Bridge, the cinematic double-loop interchange at Rongqiao Nankai Middle School, the dizzying heights of Caiyuanba Bridge, her childhood home in Geleshan Town, and late-night barbecue and bike rides along Binjiang Road in Nan’an District. These spots reveal a Chongqing of open skies, riversides, and mountain paths, far from the clichés.<br/>
<br/>
Follow @RADII_media for the ultimate city guide across Asia, uncovering underground scenes and secret spots.<br/>
<br/>
#radiimedia #radii #chongqing #cityguide #travel #china #electronicmusic #bridges #neonlights #cyberpunk</p>]]></description>
